Version 1.0 -> 2.0 ————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————

The Session Manager package has been been replaced by the Session Manager component that an exploded view is provided later in the document.

Changed the components’ organization.

Consequently other minor fixes and updates have been done in
 - DB logic view
 - Deployment view
 - Sequence diagrams
 - Interfaces

Finally, the correspondences between UX diagrams and the various components of the system have been added.

Light reorganization of the document structure.